    Description: Define the 'freebsd_pf_scrub' option.
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Arbitrary
    Type       : Array/Hash
    Default    : [{config: {'in all fragment reassemble'}, comment: 'Scrub: Incoming traffic normalization'},
